text.tspan: We can pre-book your ski hire on your behalf. This can be
delivered to your accommodation with a number of options for
you to try to ensure you get the right kit (and comfy boots!)
Or we’ll locate the easiest shop for you to get to without walking half a mile afterwards, where you can get kitted
up and browse any other accessories you might need to pick up before hitting the slopes!
All ski shops offer a range of different standard skis and snowboards from the basic bronze package through
to “top of the range” platinum level equipment. If you like to switch out of your ski boots as soon as you’re off the
slopes and hit the apres ski dance floor. Or head off to browse the market and cheese shops in your comfortable
shoes, we can also arrange ski lockers for you in the heart of the resort.
We can also pre-order your lift pases for you and have them ready and waiting for you at your accommodation.
This way you can get up and hit the slopes as soon as you're ready on your first day without long lift pass ques.
Click “here” to get in touch now and start booking
